{"tid":2102632,"cid":21,"subCid":0,"title":"第三十一屆台灣金曲獎入圍名單","createTime":"2020-07-10T15:08:52.000Z","updateTime":"2020-07-10T15:46:21.000Z","uid":53308,"like":0,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":3,"replies":[{"pid":"d52d21e24de4ab4cd8f3311a9ace7a696797aa41","tid":2102632,"uid":53308,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-07-10T15:08:52.000Z","msg":"第三十一屆台灣金曲獎<br />\n日期 : 10月3日晚上7點<br />\n地點 : 台北流行音樂文化中心<br />\n<br />\n武漢肺炎的疫情嚴峻，原定在6月舉辦的金曲獎頒獎典禮，今天宣布將延期到10月3日舉辦，入圍名單改至7月中公布，至於金曲國際音樂節系列活動則將取消辦理。"},{"pid":"27b7586b940dd6e079ca57ab66e684310b455458","tid":2102632,"uid":53308,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-07-10T15:10:04.000Z","msg":"推到娃娃拿金曲歌后<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"c04f3183d6970df4381861ea788531dac356347b","tid":2102632,"uid":78290,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"27b7586b940dd6e079ca57ab66e684310b455458","tid":2102632,"uid":53308,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-07-10T15:10:04.000Z","msg":"推到娃娃拿金曲歌后<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-07-10T15:14:25.000Z","msg":"娃娃<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"cf190b03c279914cad1bcfcbc496a6a4e75e8fac","tid":2102632,"uid":307619,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-07-10T15:37:31.000Z","msg":"瘦子<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/support.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"800eb2ce46a3a3905faa5a7488d7bb11a211c0ea","tid":2102632,"uid":53308,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-07-10T15:46:21.000Z","msg":"轉post / 轉返分類<br />\n<a href=\"https://lihkg.com/thread/2102674/page/1?post=1\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lihkg.com/thread/2102674/page/1?post=1</a>"}],"pinned":{"pid":"800eb2ce46a3a3905faa5a7488d7bb11a211c0ea","tid":2102